{"type":"message","id":"bca3361c","parentId":"beedbbe9","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:34:37.959Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-04-03 13:34 GMT-3] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Research whether ACP is likely the right runtime mechanism for this user's OpenClaw multi-agent workflow use case. Focus on: long-running agent workflows, nested agent invocation, persistent/discrete execution, and why users might fail to get agent workflows working in OpenClaw without ACP. Use local OpenClaw docs first (especially docs/cli/acp.md, docs/tools/acp-agents.md, docs/concepts/multi-agent.md, docs/tools/subagents.md, docs/cli/agents.md, docs/cli/sessions.md, docs/concepts/session.md). Then supplement with web research only if necessary. Goal: determine whether ACP is best treated as (a) standard execution substrate, (b) selective substrate, or (c) not the right fix. Provide a nuanced recommendation for the user's B2/Perseus case. Do not edit files."}],"timestamp":1775234077943}}
{"type":"message","id":"def24da2","parentId":"bca3361c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:34:41.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm a subagent tasked with researching whether ACP is the right runtime mechanism for a multi-agent workflow use case. My goal is to:\n\n1. Investigate long-running agent workflows, nested agent invocation, persistent/discrete execution\n2. Understand why users might fail with agent workflows in OpenClaw without ACP\n3. Use local OpenClaw docs first (docs/cli/acp.md, docs/tools/acp-agents.md, docs/concepts/multi-agent.md, docs/tools/subagents.md, docs/cli/agents.md, docs/cli/sessions.md, docs/concepts/session.md)\n4. Supplement with web research only if necessary\n5. Recommend whether ACP should be: (a) standard, (b) selective, or (c) not the right fix\n6. Provide nuanced recommendation for \"B2/Perseus case\" (which the requester mentioned)\n\nLet me start by exploring the local OpenClaw documentation in the order suggested.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I'll research ACP's role in OpenClaw's multi-agent workflows by reviewing the local documentation first, then provide a nuanced recommendation. Let me start by examining the key docs."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01A99SiNRWwMtzznDuck9Vht","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"docs/cli/acp.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0197qPBavimVkexDoNGnrTti","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"docs/tools/acp-agents.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01QbXnahsm82ExWEmaYGueTR","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"docs/concepts/multi-agent.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01YNSDvLnktWEdYwAiVoBXk4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"docs/tools/subagents.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":460,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":15066,"totalTokens":15536,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0023000000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.018832500000000002,"tot